    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good summary. You mentioned the benefits are \"undeniable,\" but I've been reading a lot of stuff about how it might actually hurt the local economy or just be a way to squeeze more money out of commuters. Do you think the environmental benefits actually outweigh those social/economic concerns, or is it more complicated than that?",
